  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      First line treatment for advanced ovarian carcinoma hyperthermic intraperitoneal chemotherapy
      (HIPEC) after optimal debulking.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Addition of HIPEC to the standard first line treatment of ovarian carcinoma.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
